{
  "stem": "10905.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We got off the boat finally.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And everybody wore hats in those days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Havas was there waiting for us with a straw hat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Another woman, a Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Hecht, H-E-C-H-T, who was in a-- who was in the same barrack with us on top, on the third barrack-- on the third bed and high up, who had come to the United States early, she was there waiting for us, one of my mother's cousins, and-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] were waiting.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we're very hungry, because it had been quite some time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the only way I could speak with Mr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Havas was in Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I start speaking Hungarian to him about how hungry I was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, here's this man, a vendor, who's selling, in Hungarian said, how would you like to have a ham sandwich?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, I can't believe this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What a wonderful country.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody speaks Hungarian here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Havas spoke Hungarian, and this vendor spoke Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- Were you really excited when you were coming?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, it was-- I mean, it was a-- you know, I was so seasick for two days, but after that it was just the most marvelous thing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The crossing the-- the Atlantic was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, seeing the Statue of Liberty, it didn't mean anything to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was a seven-year-old kid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Didn't mean any-- now it means a lot to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But [? personally, ?] it didn't mean-- the buildings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, I had seen the film with Joel Grey, I thought there were cowboys.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, really, you know, there were cowboys and, you know, this is nowadays, and there were cowboys and [? people, ?] horses.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
